00:43:06,584 --> 00:43:08,836
I was just out on the back
porch for a second.

554
00:43:09,378 --> 00:43:11,380
The convention's great.

555
00:43:14,675 --> 00:43:16,219
I said it's great!

556
00:43:16,469 --> 00:43:18,012
Actually, the competition's...

